Air Force One can kind of make a proper

01:08.344 --> 01:11.934
trip. And so I had tweeted this joke

01:11.982 --> 01:15.950
out and AJ. Replied and was like, I'm going to make that a reality.

01:16.110 --> 01:20.178
I was like, okay. Yeah, he's got this company. He's got some cool renders.

