01:30.848 --> 01:34.874
believe he's going to do it. And he's actually tracking his progress to

01:34.992 --> 01:38.614
the speed at which Lockheed Martin Skunkworks Division built the SR

01:38.662 --> 01:42.358
71. And he's trying to build a plane faster than

01:42.384 --> 01:47.630
they did, which is incredible because it's one of, like, the historical incredible

01:47.970 --> 01:51.726
projects like the Manhattan Project that just happened so quickly. And we

01:51.748 --> 01:55.394
