you know, I've toured the facility. I spent a full day there

02:03.928 --> 02:07.554
in Atlanta, and I met with all the co founders, saw everything

02:07.592 --> 02:10.934
in facility, and it was just a fascinating experience. So I'm excited to

02:11.052 --> 02:14.262
tell you about it. And I've actually done a few videos on YouTube about

02:14.396 --> 02:17.606
supersonic technology in the past. One was about

02:17.628 --> 02:20.850
the SR 71, and then the other one was about this company, Boom, which is

02:20.860 --> 02:24.470
a Y combinator company. They've raised a bunch of money and they're making a supersonic

02:24.550 --> 02:28.282
jetliner for commercial air flight. And it's a very, very different

02:28.336 --> 02:31.546
approach. Boom. As you'll see with the story. Like they're going

